; _dev_screenshots/extracted_overlay.png for the pixel→world extraction).
; FloorPlateNode supports slanted floors via YLeft/YRight; where dy ≠ 0
; the slant is honoured in GetYAt() and in the debug bar rotation.
; ShowDebug=false for normal play; flip on only while re-placing floor plates.

