; ── Elevator ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; Yellow rectangle from the user's mark-up: BL=(-14.53, 2.14), TR=(-12.49,
; 5.52). Shaft sits at x ≈ -13.5, lifting between the low floor (y=2.08)
; and the slanted floor (y≈5.36 at that x). This is the only unreachable
; pocket in the painting — everywhere else is stair-connected.
